General.Name: Korvest Ltd
General.Description: Korvest Ltd, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the hot dip galvanizing and sheet metal fabrication businesses in Australia. It operates through two segments, Industrial Products and Production. The Industrial Products segment manufactures electrical and cable support systems, which include channel, cable trays, cable ladders, cable mesh and ducts, and general and heavy duty pipe clamps and hangers, as well as specialist pipe supports products, other fittings, fasteners, and clamping components under the EzyStrut name. The Production segment provides hot dip galvanizing services. The company is also involved in the manufacture of cable and pipe support systems, and fittings. It serves infrastructure, commercial, utilities, mining, food processing, oil and gas, power stations, health, and industrial sectors. The company was incorporated in 1970 and is based in Kilburn, Australia.
